quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  113,1,"ql -ayha alrasul-: 'aeudh wa'aetasim birabi alfaliq, wahu alsbh"
  113,2,min sharu jmye almakhluqat wa'adhahua
  113,3,"wimin shara layl shadid alzalmat 'iidha dakhal wataghlghul, wama fih min alshurur walmudhiat"
  113,4,wmin shari alssahirat allaati ynfkhn fima yaeqadun min euqad biqasd alsihar
  113,5,"wimin sharin hasid mubaghad lilnaas 'iidha hasadahum ealaa ma wahabahum allah min nem, wa'arad zawalaha eanhum, wa'iiqae al'adhaa bihm"